As for areas to improve on, Danny could be a bit more assertive. Sometimes communication over email or slack is sufficient enough but there are occasions when he could have tried to get the persons attention rather than waiting for a response that could take hours/days. Another area is asking questions. Danny should structure them in a way that explains the issue and steps he's taken to try to solve it. There were occasions when the person had to question Danny to understand the full scope of the problem.

Danny will make a great software engineer. He¿s shown interest in web development over the past couple of weeks and is willing to stick with the team. But he has also expressed his interest in developing on hardware solutions. I¿m not sure if we have a role available in that area but if we do, I¿m sure Danny will do well in that team.






